dct_description_sm: Map of South Amboy and insets of Old Bridge and Dayton (South Brunswick Township). Names of property owners listed. Existing and proposed wharfs are shown. Removed from Everts and Stewart's Combination Atlas map of Middlesex County, N.J., 1876, plates 80 and 81.
